    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<sect1 id="group__nusol__cuda_1nusol_overview">
<title>Overview</title>
<para>The NuSol module implements algorithms for reconstructing neutrino momenta in semi-leptonic and di-leptonic top quark decays. This is essential for ttbar physics analyses.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="group__nusol__cuda_1nusol_functions">
<title>Available Functions</title>
