<sect1 id="group__nusol__cuda_1nusol_algorithm">
<title>Algorithm</title>
<para>The neutrino reconstruction uses the following constraints:</para>
<para><orderedlist>
<listitem><para><bold>W boson mass constraint</bold>: m(lν) = m_W</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><bold>Top quark mass constraint</bold>: m(blν) = m_t</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><bold>Missing ET constraint</bold>: Σpx(ν) = MET_x, Σpy(ν) = MET_y</para>
</listitem></orderedlist>
</para>
<para>For single neutrino (semi-leptonic):<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Uses W and top mass constraints</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Solves quadratic equation for pz(ν)</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para>For double neutrino (di-leptonic):<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Uses both W mass constraints</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Uses MET constraint</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Solves system of equations iteratively</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="group__nusol__cuda_1nusol_example">
<title>Example</title>
<para><programlisting filename=".cpp"><codeline><highlight class="preprocessor">#include<sp/>&lt;<ref refid="nusol_8cuh" kindref="compound">nusol/nusol.cuh</ref>&gt;</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Semi-leptonic<sp/>reconstruction</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">torch::Tensor<sp/>pmc_b<sp/>=<sp/>...;<sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>b-jet<sp/>4-momentum</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">torch::Tensor<sp/>pmc_mu<sp/>=<sp/>...;<sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>lepton<sp/>4-momentum</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">torch::Tensor<sp/>met_xy<sp/>=<sp/>...;<sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Missing<sp/>ET<sp/>(x,<sp/>y)</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">torch::Tensor<sp/>masses<sp/>=<sp/>...;<sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>[m_top,<sp/>m_W,<sp/>m_nu]</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">torch::Tensor<sp/>sigma<sp/>=<sp/>...;<sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>MET<sp/>resolution</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="keyword">auto</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>result<sp/>=<sp/><ref refid="namespacenusol___1a6f05175e14627bd3c34ffa61686b7da4" kindref="member">nusol_::Nu</ref>(&amp;pmc_b,<sp/>&amp;pmc_mu,<sp/>&amp;met_xy,<sp/>&amp;masses,<sp/>&amp;sigma,<sp/>1e-10);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">torch::Tensor<sp/>nu_momentum<sp/>=<sp/>result[</highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;nu&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal">];</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">torch::Tensor<sp/><ref refid="combinatorial_8cxx_1acd33f38fd89cd298ef5d1ea858ee0416" kindref="member">chi2</ref><sp/>=<sp/>result[</highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;chi2&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal">];</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="group__nusol__cuda_1nusol_combinatorial">
<title>Combinatorial Reconstruction</title>
<para>For events with ambiguous jet-lepton assignments, the <computeroutput><ref refid="classcombinatorial" kindref="compound">combinatorial()</ref></computeroutput> function tests all possible combinations:</para>
<para><programlisting filename=".cpp"><codeline><highlight class="keyword">auto</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>result<sp/>=<sp/>nusol_::combinatorial(</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>&amp;<ref refid="enums_8h_1a71db5b98a8935886920bcc7eaaf49fb9aeaef5a1a889ab3d077c4cbb1bf789bf7" kindref="member">edge_index</ref>,<sp/>&amp;batch,<sp/>&amp;<ref refid="enums_8h_1a666fa98df084d96fc481369704153b28a04130da60e65c7800006cd7886515b56" kindref="member">pmc</ref>,<sp/>&amp;pid,<sp/>&amp;met_xy,</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>172.62*1000,<sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>m_top<sp/>in<sp/>MeV</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>80.385*1000,<sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>m_W<sp/>in<sp/>MeV</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>1e-10,<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>null<sp/>threshold</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>1e-3,<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>perturbation</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>100,<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>max<sp/>steps</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keyword">false</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>units<sp/>(false<sp/>=<sp/>MeV,<sp/>true<sp/>=<sp/>GeV)</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">);</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting> </para>
</sect1>
